{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-335-gathering-the-beans","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 335: Sakupljanje pasulja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Svaki put kada Peteru postane dosadno, on postavlja nekoliko činija, svaku sa jednim zrnom pasulja, u krug. Zatim uzima sva zrna iz određene činije i spušta ih jedno po jedno u činije koje se nalaze u smeru kazaljke na satu. Nastavlja ovo, počevši od činije u koju je spustio poslednje zrno, sve dok se početno stanje ponovo ne pojavi. Na primer, za 5 činija radi sledeće:</p>\n<img alt=\"animation of moving beans in 5 bowls\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/gathering-the-beans.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Za 5 činija, Peteru je potrebno 15 koraka da se vrati u početno stanje.</p>\n<p>Neka $M(x)$ predstavlja broj koraka potrebnih za povratak u početno stanje, počevši od činije $x$. Dakle, $M(5) = 15$. Takođe se može dokazati da je $M(100) = 10920$.</p>\n<p>Tafuta $\\displaystyle\\sum_{k = 0}^{{10}^{18}} M(2^k + 1)$. Toa jibu lako modulo $7^9$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4bd1000cf542c50ffce","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301993,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-335-gathering-the-beans"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function gatheringTheBeans() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ngatheringTheBeans();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>gatheringTheBeans()</code> should return <code>5032316</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(gatheringTheBeans(), 5032316);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-335-gathering-the-beans","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-336-maximix-arrangements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-334-spilling-the-beans","id":"5900f4bd1000cf542c50ffce","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-335-gathering-the-beans"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}